          the scroll.
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="fade-up-3 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/60 max-w-sm sm:max-w-lg mb-5 sm:mb-6">
          Sophomore studying Digital Communication Media &amp; Multimedia — building campaigns, flyers, and ads with intention.
        </p>
        <button onclick="goTo('#work')" class="fade-up-4 rounded-lg bg-white px-5 py-2.5 sm:px-6 sm:py-3 text-sm font-medium text-black hover:scale-105 transition-transform inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          View My Work <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="overflow-hidden py-3 bg-[#17140F] border-b border-[#E4DAC2]/20">
    <div class="marquee-track flex gap-8 text-sm tracking-wide uppercase whitespace-nowrap text-white/50">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-8">
        <span>Sophomore</span><span class="text-[var(--rose)]">•</span>
        <span>Digital Communication Media &amp; Multimedia</span><span class="text-[var(--tape)]">•</span>
        <span>Graphic Designer</span><span class="text-[var(--rose)]">•</span>
      </span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-8">
        <span>Sophomore</span><span class="text-[var(--rose)]">•</span>
        <span>Digital Communication Media &amp; Multimedia</span><span class="text-[var(--tape)]">•</span>
