  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about" class="px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-28 lg:px-16 bg-[var(--paper)]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 text-[var(--rose)]">About</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium leading-snug mb-6 text-[var(--ink)]">
        Hi, I'm Simran — a graphic designer who likes it when design and strategy sit at the same table.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 text-[var(--muted)]">
        I'm a sophomore majoring in Digital Communication Media &amp; Multimedia, and I care about the same
        question at every scale: what makes someone stop and look? Sometimes that's a poster in a hallway,
        sometimes it's a caption in a feed. I'm building my toolkit through Adobe's Digital Marketing and
        Social Media Content &amp; Strategy specialization, an Adobe Digital Marketing Strategy specialization,
        and Meta's Social Media Marketing program — alongside coursework in visual storytelling and multimedia.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--muted)]">
        Outside of class, I design flyers, ads, and campaigns for real briefs — including a full admissions
        campaign for a school in India — because I'd rather learn by shipping than just studying theory.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <span class="tape-chip text-xs sm:text-sm px-4 py-2 shadow-[2px_2px_0_rgba(23,20,15,0.1)]" style="background-color:var(--tape); color:var(--ink); transform:rotate(-2deg);">Adobe Digital Marketing &amp; Social Media Content and Strategy</span>
        <span class="tape-chip text-xs sm:text-sm px-4 py-2 shadow-[2px_2px_0_rgba(23,20,15,0.1)]" style="background-color:var(--tape); color:var(--ink); transform:rotate(2deg);">Adobe Digital Marketing Strategy Specialization</span>
        <span class="tape-chip text-xs sm:text-sm px-4 py-2 shadow-[2px_2px_0_rgba(23,20,15,0.1)]" style="background-color:var(--tape); color:var(--ink); transform:rotate(-2deg);">Meta Social Media Marketing</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

